&#039;Konk&#039; is the second album from Brighton-based indie-popsters The 
Kooks. Produced at Ray Davies famous studio of the same name, the 
album is a sprightly-yet-assured follow-up to the platinum-selling 
&#039;Inside In/Inside Out&#039;. Includes the single &#039;Always Where I Need To 
Be&#039;. This limited version includes seven additional brand new
 compositions.
